companyName: Plural Industry Holding Group Co. Limited
description: Plural Industry Holding Group Co. Limited, a development stage company, focuses on developing and operating Internet domain names in the budget travel and related categories. The company was formerly known as Enabling Asia, Inc. and changed its name to Plural Industry Holding Group Co. Limited in June 2021. Plural Industry Holding Group Co. Limited is based in Oceanside, New York.
